	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non scripturus fueram, d. pater; proxime fueram gratias acturus pro tuis tot officiis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed ecce heri vesperi dicitur quidam Mediolano advenisse, qui dixisse fertur <persName type="auto_name">Hannibalis</persName> copias omnes pessum isse, <persName type="auto_name">Hannibalem</persName> captum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hodie veniunt literae d. consuli <persName type="auto_name">Ambrosio Bellizona</persName> a certo viro, in quibus nunciatur illas copias tempestate periisse et quidem in universum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc, quid verum sit, audiemus brevi; existimo rem non omni carere fide.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Addit ille in suis ad consulem literis <placeName type="auto_name">Genuenses</placeName> in maximo periculo versari, quod quidem <persName ref="p19981" cert="high">S. Petro</persName> <persName type="auto_name">Corso</persName> nomine ab ipsis ad <placeName type="auto_name">Turcam</placeName> defecerit et oppidum in <placeName type="auto_name">Corsica</placeName> ceperit.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Congruunt hęc cum d. <persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Bezae</persName> literis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Addit praeterea <placeName type="auto_name">Genuenses</placeName> misisse certos homines cum mandatis Mediolanum, ut ibi militem novum pararent; sed Mediolanensibus militia interdictum poena capitali.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Doch so sygind die houptlütt und andere befelchslütt or dem verbott schon darvon gesyn.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec subito te scire volui et dubito, an sit, cui dare possim literas; existimo enim nostros iam abiisse.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale, reverende pater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Calendis augusti <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curię</placeName> anno 1564.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName type="auto_name">F[abritius</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Amplissimo viro d. Heinrycho Bullingero, domino suo colendissimo.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
